rComments: My main reservation about this professor was the fact that his English is not the greatest. However, he does understand the material very well, and his powerpoints contain almost everything you need. Once I figured out the fundamental concepts of the course it came down to basic math and memorizing graphs. Didn't think I would get an A, but I did.

He is a amazing professor!! He is helpful and is always there to answer your questions. He even gives bonus marks for attendance and answering the question which is are easy marks. One of the best profs I have ever had.
he is a very nice professor and also has a sense of humor sometime.
